"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/837589","Ministry of Justice","false","2018-02-08","<p>The Ministry of Justice carried out a call for evidence on corporate criminal liability for economic crime in 2017, to establish whether further reform of the law was necessary. The response will issue in due course.</p>","South East Cambridgeshire","Lucy Frazer","126710","2018-02-08T17:08:30.797Z",,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/837589/answer","Biography information for Lucy Frazer","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/837589/answer",,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/837589/answer",,,,,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2018-02-05","Business: Fraud","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, on what date he plans to publish the outcome of the call for evidence on corporate liability for economic crime.","false","Biography information for Helen Goodman","Bishop Auckland","Helen Goodman","126708"
